            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1683217863951-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>While the pepper is cooking, wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1683217868635-x200.jpg",
