            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1683217868635-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has started to soften, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>ground turmeric </strong>to the pan with your<strong> curry powder</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683217873856-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683217873856-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683217873856-x700.jpg",
